;s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"semrush integration\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=30300\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:514:\"<p>Do you want to maximize your rankings in search engines and grow your organic traffic by ranking for more keywords with your content? AlOSEO now seamlessly integrates with Semrush’s additional keyphrase feature. Now you can easily find more keyphrases and add them to your content in a single click.</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-semrush-integration/\">Introducing Semrush Integration: Add Additional Keyphrases to Boost SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Stina Pettersson\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6278:\"<p>Do you want to maximize your rankings in search engines and grow your organic traffic by ranking for more keywords with your content?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today we&#8217;re excited to announce we&#8217;ve made it easier than ever to rank for related or additional keyphrases with our new Semrush integration!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AlOSEO now seamlessly integrates with Semrush’s additional keyphrase feature. Now you can easily find more keyphrases and add them to your content in a single click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s take a closer look…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Everything Starts With the Search Intent</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, Google doesn&#8217;t just match what people search for word-for-word. It aims to understand the meaning or intent behind the words.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why stuffing content with the same main keyword over and over again just won&#8217;t work anymore.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead, it&#8217;s important to create quality content that uses related keywords and keyphrases. This helps Google to understand the meaning behind your content, and match it with more searches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The more related keyword variations you use in your content, the more searches you can rank for, and the more traffic you&#8217;ll unlock!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Start Ranking in Search Engines for Additional Keyphrases</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Together with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Semrush</a>, we’ve now built an integration that helps you find additional related keyphrases for your focus keyphrase in AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s super easy! Let&#8217;s give you a sneak peak.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Simply scroll down in the post or page you’re editing below your Focus Keyphrase and click on the Get Additional Keyphrases button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"419\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/get-additional-keyphrases-in-all-in-one-seo.png\" alt=\"Introducing Semrush integration - get additional keyphrases in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-30301\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/get-additional-keyphrases-in-all-in-one-seo.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/get-additional-keyphrases-in-all-in-one-seo-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/get-additional-keyphrases-in-all-in-one-seo-600x344.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This will open a new window where you can log in or create your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Semrush </a>account.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/connect-to-semrush.png\" alt=\"Introducing Semrush integration - log in or create a Semrush account\" class=\"wp-image-30302\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/connect-to-semrush.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/connect-to-semrush-300x187.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/connect-to-semrush-600x373.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, approve access to Semrush, and bam! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best of all, it&#8217;s free for everyone! Plus you can upgrade to get even more!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is how simple it is to add related keyphrases with our Semrush integration. It even gives you the search volume and trends straight from the screen:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"359\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-by-semrush.png\" alt=\"Introducing Semrush integration - add keyphrase \" class=\"wp-image-30305\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-by-semrush.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-by-semrush-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-by-semrush-600x295.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With a single click on the Add Keyphrase button, the keyphrase will be added to your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Finding related keywords can’t get easier than that!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There&#8217;s more&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230;after adding a keyphrase, AIOSEO gives you feedback on your new keyphrase and&nbsp;recommendations on what you need to improve, as well as what you’ve done well to maximize your rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"391\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-seo-analysis.png\" alt=\"SEO analysis of additional keyphrases in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-30306\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-seo-analysis.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-seo-analysis-300x161.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/additional-keyphrases-seo-analysis-600x321.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you’ll enjoy our new Semrush integration. In adding this feature, our goal was to help make it easy for you to discover new related keywords that you can use to improve your content and boost rankings on Google and other search engines.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s all for today, but there are always exciting things happening at All In One SEO as we continually strive to create the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\">best SEO plugin for WordPress</a>. Keep your eyes on the blog for future updates!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not using <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\">All in One SEO</a> yet?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons aligncenter\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button u-pl0\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-theme-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" style=\"background-color:#009966\" rel=\"\"><span class=\"has-inline-color has-theme-background-color\">Get Started with AIOSEO Today!</span></a></div>\n</div>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-semrush-integration/\">Introducing Semrush Integration: Add Additional Keyphrases to Boost SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s